snippet: Derail Green and Jontrell Walker combined for 44 points as Incarnate Word (4-5) defeated St. John’s (7-4), 73-51, handing the Red Storm their first home loss this season.
abstract: Incarnate Word beats St Johns, 73-51; other college basketball news noted.
